column5: Leaving on Sat. 7/31 for Lac Seul. Looking for MOST RECENT update on road construction on Hwy 502? How many miles are gravel and single lane? What type of delays to expect? Also, wondering about any delays on causeway bridge over Rainy Lake? Trying to decide if we should take Hwy 71 or not. Thanks for your input!
502 is clear all the way, the bridge has a 3-10min wait depending what time you go over it.
Is it all repaved or are there still gravel stretches?
All paved, working on the shoulder, 5 minute delay on Wednesday at 4pm on 502, 5 minutes at the bridge.
Thanks for the update, looks like we will take 502! Leaving tomorrow for Lac Seul! Yahoo! RBF
Where are you staying on lac Seul??
Fisherman's Cove in Scout Bay. Are you going too?
Fisherman Cove is a nice place. We just got back from Lac Seul Lodge, just North of you. Good Luck.
